text: Zoe Swicord Kazan (born September 9, 1983) is an American actress, playwright, and screenwriter. She is known for her roles in The Savages (2007), Revolutionary Road (2008) and It's Complicated (2009). In 2014, she appeared in the HBO miniseries Olive Kitteridge, for which she received an Emmy nomination. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:American playwrights Category:Yale University alumni Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:Screenwriters from Los Angeles
